│ 16357 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles emission,                                                                                                    │
│ 16358 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is actually                                                                                                       │
│ 16359 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the                                                                                                       │
│ 16360 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further                                                                                                    │
│ 16361 /// analysis/transformations.                                                                                                                                                       │
